  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "**Is this a bug report or feature request?**\r\n* Bug Report\r\n\r\n**Deviation from expected behavior:**\r\nPVC is stuck in pending state.\r\n\r\n**Environment**:\r\n* Rook version: v1.0.0-597.g5c59a1e\r\n* Storage backend version: v14.2.2-20190722\r\n* Kubernetes version: v1.15.3\r\n\r\nI get a lot of RBAC-related errors in logs:\r\n\r\n- `kubectl logs -n rook-ceph csi-rbdplugin-provisioner-68f5664455-8wtxm csi-provisioner`\r\n```\r\nI0904 19:09:41.754451       1 leaderelection.go:222] failed to acquire lease rook-ceph/rook-ceph-rbd-csi-ceph-com\r\nE0904 19:09:51.785532       1 leaderelection.go:306] error retrieving resource lock rook-ceph/rook-ceph-rbd-csi-ceph-com: leases.coordination.k8s.io \"rook-ceph-rbd-csi-ceph-com\" is forbidden: User \"system:serviceaccount:rook-ceph:rook-csi-rbd-provisioner-sa\" cannot get resource \"leases\" in API group \"coordination.k8s.io\" in the namespace \"rook-ceph\"\r\n```\r\n- `kubectl logs -n rook-ceph rook-ceph-operator-6d8fb98596-gzlvr`\r\n```\r\nE0904 19:06:43.635603       7 reflector.go:126] sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/cache/internal/informers_map.go:126: Failed to list *v1beta1.PodDisruptionBudget: poddisruptionbudgets.policy is forbidden: User \"system:serviceaccount:rook-ceph:rook-ceph-system\" cannot list resource \"poddisruptionbudgets\" in API group \"policy\" at the cluster scope\r\nE0904 19:06:43.737339       7 reflector.go:126] github.com/kube-object-storage/lib-bucket-provisioner/pkg/client/informers/externalversions/factory.go:117: Failed to list *v1alpha1.ObjectBucketClaim: objectbucketclaims.objectbucket.io is forbidden: User \"system:serviceaccount:rook-ceph:rook-ceph-system\" cannot list resource \"objectbucketclaims\" in API group \"objectbucket.io\" at the cluster scope\r\nE0904 19:06:43.834851       7 reflector.go:126] sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/cache/internal/informers_map.go:126: Failed to list *v1.Deployment: deployments.apps is forbidden: User \"system:serviceaccount:rook-ceph:rook-ceph-system\" cannot list resource \"deployments\" in API group \"apps\" at the cluster scope\r\nE0904 19:06:44.643900       7 reflector.go:126] github.com/kube-object-storage/lib-bucket-provisioner/pkg/client/informers/externalversions/factory.go:117: Failed to list *v1alpha1.ObjectBucket: objectbuckets.objectbucket.io is forbidden: User \"system:serviceaccount:rook-ceph:rook-ceph-system\" cannot list resource \"objectbuckets\" in API group \"objectbucket.io\" at the cluster scope\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf I apply `common.yaml`, then everything works as expected.\r\n\r\nOn a cursory look I found that `rbd-external-provisioner-cfg` role is missing `coordination.k8s.io` rule, but there are probably more discrepancies.\r\n\r\n",
